HB 569 Original 2026 Regular Session Turner
Appropriates $17,000 out of the State General Fund (Direct) for FY 2025-2026 for payment
of the consent judgment against the state in the suit captioned Anna Flowers and Brent
Flowers v. State of La. et als., bearing No. 63,977, on the docket of the 11th Judicial District,
Sabine Parish.
Proposed law provides relative to payment. Provides relative to conflicts between judgment
and proposed law. Prohibits accrual of interest on the judgment as of the effective date of
proposed law.
Effective upon signature of governor or lapse of time for gubernatorial action.
